### Composition

The intricacies of local politics are perhaps best illustrated by the precise, and often fragmented, composition of the council. Following the electoral contest of [2022](/2022_Wrexham_County_Borough_Council_election), and accounting for the inevitable, if somewhat predictable, shifts in allegiance that occurred up to August 2025, the council's 56 seats were distributed among various political groupings as follows: &#91;24&#93; &#91;25&#93; &#91;26&#93;

